title: Converse Rubber Tracks: Ready, Set - The Hundred in the Hands perform "Faded"
description:
During NXNE The Hundred in the Hands stopped by the pop-up Converse Rubber Tracks studio in Toronto for a live performance of "Faded".

To learn more visit: http://www.converse.com/rubbertracks
